OL,3,CArmy admits it 'failed' soldier who
OL,4,Cdied in training exercise crash
OL,6,FArmy bosses have admitted they "didn't
OL,7,Fdo enough" to protect a solider who
OL,8,Fwas killed in a vehicle crash at the
OL,9,Fcountry's largest garrison.
OL,11,FStaff Sergeant John McKelvie was
OL,12,Fkilled after the Jackal vehicle he was
OL,13,Fdriving rolled multiple times down a
OL,14,Fsteep hill at Catterick Garrison in
OL,15,FJanuary 2019.
OL,17,FAt the time of the incident, the 51-
OL,18,Fyear-old had been taking part in
OL,19,Ftraining on land nicknamed The Land of
OL,20,FNod during which his vehicle lost
OL,21,Ftraction and rolled backwards.
