OL,3,CArmy admits it 'failed' soldier who
OL,4,Cdied in training exercise crash
OL,6,FHe sustained serious injuries and was
OL,7,Fairlifted to hospital, where he died
OL,8,Fsix days later.
OL,10,FOn Thursday the Health and Safety
OL,11,FExecutive said it had issued the
OL,12,FMinistry of Defence with a Crown
OL,13,FCensure - the maximum penalty it can
OL,14,Fimpose on a government body.
OL,16,FArmy spokesman General Roly Walker
OL,17,Fsaid he accepted the findings, adding:
OL,18,F"I apologise unreservedly for failing
OL,19,Fto maintain the safety standards
OL,20,Frightly expected of the British Army.
