OL,3,CArmy admits it 'failed' soldier who
OL,4,Cdied in training exercise crash
OL,6,F"Staff Sergeant John McKelvie died
OL,7,Fbecause we didn't do enough to protect
OL,8,Fhim from the risk of death."
OL,10,FThe HSE found risk assessments at
OL,11,FCatterick were "not suitable and
OL,12,Fsufficient".
OL,14,FIt said the training course Mr
OL,15,FMcKelvie was on involved hazardous
OL,16,Factivities and the risk of the vehicle
OL,17,Frolling.
