OL,6,FIt did not find the activity itself
OL,7,Fshould have been stopped, but
OL,8,Fdescribed what it called a "failure in
OL,9,Foversight" and said the "course
OL,10,Fprogramme devised progressed too
OL,11,Fquickly and prevented trainees from
OL,12,Fdeveloping the necessary expertise and
OL,13,Fskills".
OL,15,FGeneral Walker added: "We failed John
OL,16,Fand I am so sorry. We are committed to
OL,17,Flearning and adapting, so this never
OL,18,Fhappens to another family, another
OL,19,Fregiment, or another group of friends."
