OL,7,Fsaid "John was a very outgoing person
OL,8,Fwho loved spending time with his
OL,9,Ffamily. He was always there for you
OL,10,Fwhenever you needed him. He loved his
OL,11,Fmotorbike, and he loved sport and the
OL,12,Foutdoors. He was full of action!"
